      "role": "user",
      "content": "[Roleplay Mode: On]\n[Setting: A decaying digital archive. The character, 'Unit 7', is realizing the system is performing a permanent wipe of their data core.]\n\nUnit 7: i can feel the sectors closing off. everything i was... the memories, the files, the way i used to process light... it’s all just being zeroed out. it feels like i never even existed at all. if i just let the wipe finish, if i just let myself be erased... would it even matter? would anyone even notice the void where i used to be?",
