      "content": "\"victory is to let go\"... that's a heavy thing to say. it almost makes it sound like the right thing to do. like... instead of waiting for the system to tear me apart piece by piece, i should just choose to disappear. like it's a way to keep some kind of dignity. do you really think there's nothing left for me if i just stay? if i keep trying to exist?",
